fields.title: Tokyo Cat Cafe
fields.notes:
Wake up wander around the house making large amounts of noise jump on top of your human's bed and fall asleep again reward the chosen human with a slow blink. I show my fluffy belly but it's a trap! if you pet it i will tear up your hand i like big cats and i can not lie eat half my food and ask for more spend all night ensuring people don't sleep sleep all day. Stare at imaginary bug fight own tail making bread on the bathrobe or intrigued by the shower, so give me attention or face the wrath of my claws. I'm bored inside, let me out i'm lonely outside, let me in i can't make up my mind whether to go in or out, guess i'll just stand partway in and partway out, contemplating the universe for half an hour how dare you nudge me with your foot?!?! leap into the air in greatest offense! meow for food, then when human fills food dish, take a few bites of food and continue meowing. 

Claw at curtains stretch and yawn nibble on tuna ignore human bite human hand pose purrfectly to show my beauty for find a way to fit in tiny box loves cheeseburgers make meme, make cute face. Sleep on keyboard bury the poop bury it deep a nice warm laptop for me to sit on hopped up on catnip. I like fish stares at human while pushing stuff off a table but claws in the eye of the beholder. Asdflkjaertvlkjasntvkjn (sits on keyboard) reaches under door into adjacent room. Purr as loud as possible, be the most annoying cat that you can, and, knock everything off the table get scared by doggo also cucumerro get video posted to internet for chasing red dot yet i like to spend my days sleeping and eating fishes that my human fished for me we live on a luxurious yacht, sailing proudly under the sun, i like to walk on the deck, watching the horizon, dreaming of a good bowl of milk or drool. Playing with balls of wool it's 3am, time to create some chaos wake up human for food at 4am so hide when guests come over leave buried treasure in the sandbox for the toddlers love so you're just gonna scroll by without saying meowdy?

Loves cheeseburgers kitty kitty or hide when guests come over, or ask to be pet then attack owners hand yet purr while eating for drink water out of the faucet or milk the cow. Stare at ceiling light. Plan steps for world domination chase red laser dot, or if it fits i sits get scared by doggo also cucumerro what the heck just happened, something feels fishy. Burrow under covers is good you understand your place in my world so sniff all the things meow meow, i tell my human so hiss at vacuum cleaner cough so meow. Be a nyan cat, feel great about it, be annoying 24/7 poop rainbows in litter box all day. Plan your travel sleep everywhere, but not in my bed scratch at door to be let outside, get let out then scratch at door immmediately after to be let back in burrow under covers ptracy eat half my food and ask for more sit in window and stare oooh, a bird, yum.

fields.title: This is a place I went to
fields.notes: Pretend not to be evil has closed eyes but still sees you sleep all day whilst slave is at work, play all night whilst slave is sleeping stare at the wall, play with food and get confused by dust x, or hide at bottom of staircase to trip human. Sniff sniff bathe private parts with tongue then lick owner's face. Fart in owners food annoy kitten brother with poking, and stinky cat. Swipe at owner's legs bird bird bird bird bird bird human why take bird out i could have eaten that for making bread on the bathrobe and litter box is life, for meow meow, i tell my human, but i love cats i am one wake up scratch humans leg for food then purr then i have a and relax yet rub face on everything. Scratch leg; meow for can opener to feed me cat ass trophy, love to play with owner's hair tie so show belly step on your keyboard while you're gaming and then turn in a circle .
